"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?5/58/6057?source=related_link\">",
"      Overview of the clinical manifestations, diagnosis, and management of patients with brain metastases",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?15/12/15558?source=related_link\">",
